# probe_state runtime artefacts (regenerated each run; not source)
# Snapshots: state_snapshot_<TS>.json + STATE_REPORT_<TS>.md
# Worker dirs: p2_worker_<n>/ from --workers N runs
# E2E run dirs: p2_e2e_<serial|parallel>/
# Baselines for --diff are kept (baseline.json is tracked).
